# UI smoke test — ${REPO}

> Versioned, end-to-end manual for the user-facing surface of this project.
> Treated as part of the user-facing-surface contract (per
> [AGENTS.md operating clarification #20](../../AGENTS.md#smoke-test-playbook-contract)),
> not as separate docs work.
>
> **Stale rows are themselves a doc bug.** When a PR adds or changes a
> user-facing flow, this file must move in the same PR. The `adversary`
> subagent's **Smoke-test sync** dimension flags PRs that touch
> user-facing surfaces but leave this file unchanged.

